The `create` call auto-pings {{TENANT_PERSON_FIRST_NAME}}: 📌 *Committed* — Draft Acme proposal v2 · `t-20260430-XXXX` · _due 2026-05-02_

**Narrate progress — every state change pings {{TENANT_PERSON_FIRST_NAME}}:**

